    excerpt: 'Compare full-service junk removal with dumpster rental, costs, convenience, and the right choice for your project size in Tempe and the East Valley.',
    category: 'costs',
    categoryLabel: 'Costs & Comparisons',
    categoryColor: 'bg-green-100 text-green-800',
    readTime: '8 min read',
    date: 'March 2025',
    icon: 'M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z',
  },
  {
    slug: 'how-much-does-junk-removal-cost-arizona',
    title: 'How Much Does Junk Removal Cost in Arizona?',
    excerpt: 'Transparent pricing breakdown for Tempe, Phoenix, and the East Valley. Understand flat-rate vs load-based pricing and what affects your final bill.',
    category: 'costs',
    categoryLabel: 'Costs & Comparisons',
    categoryColor: 'bg-green-100 text-green-800',
    readTime: '7 min read',
    date: 'March 2025',
    icon: 'M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z',
  },
  {
    slug: 'eco-friendly-junk-disposal-tempe-arizona',
    title: 'Eco-Friendly Junk Disposal in Tempe, Arizona',
